page.title: 17TRANSPORT
page.content: IN THE{LUTHRIE}AND{MOONZIE}AREA{HALF THE POPULATION HAVE{CARS}WHICH THEY USE FOR{WORK}AND{PLEASURE.}ABOUT {TWELVE}PEOPLE USE THE{BUS}OF WHICH{TEN USE IT FOR{PLEASURE.}THE REMAINING{TWO USE IT FOR{WORK.}A{FEW}PEOPLE USE{VANS AND{SCOOTERS}FOR{WORK}AND{PLEASURE, AND ABOUT{15}PEOPLE USE{BICYCLES.}THE PEOPLE NEED{TRANSPORT}FOR GOING TO WORK BECAUSE VERY FEW PEOPLE WORK IN AND AROUND{LUTHRIE}AND{MOONZIE. THERE ARE{TWO BUS SERVICES}IN THIS AREA;{ONE}IS A{REGIONAL COUNCIL YELLOW {MINI BUS}WHICH IS{RARELY}USED WHICH COMES ON{TUESDAY}FROM{BLEBO CRAIGS}TO {CUPAR}VIA{LUTHRIE.}ON{THURSDAYS}THE MINIBUS GOES FROM{LUTHRIE}TO{WORMIT. THE OTHER IS A{RED SERVICE BUS}RUN BY A LOCAL COMPANY WHICH GOES TO {CUPAR,DUNDEE}AND{NEWBURGH.
